Among the following rests, which one does not have a compound dotted duration?

A. <image 1>
B. <image 2>
C. <image 3>
D. <image 4>

D. <image 4>

The rest in image 4 is a simple whole note (♩, which does not have a compound dotted duration. The other rests in images 1, 2, and 3 are compound dotted notes, meaning they have a dotted duration.
